; RFC-0056 Phase 1B — extract Keeper_skill_routing leaf module from flat
; masc_mcp namespace. Stacked on Phase 1A (lib/trajectory/).
;
; Keeper_skill_routing is dependency-leaf: only stdlib (List, Printf,
; String) and masc_core (String_util). 215 LoC, fan-in ~9 bare + 1
; wrapped caller — small enough that the qualifier-removal delta stays
; trivial (RFC-0056 §3.1 G5 budget).
;
; (include_subdirs no) opts out of parent's (include_subdirs unqualified).
; (wrapped false) keeps the top-level identifier `Keeper_skill_routing`
; unchanged for bare callers — only `Keeper_skill_routing.X`
; sites in tests need prefix removal.
(include_subdirs no)

